data.description: Move right into this 2 bed, 1.5 bath unit at the desirable Georgetown Condominiums! Simple living at it's finest! Enjoy mornings eating breakfast at the peninsula of the eat in kitchen, which offers plenty of cabinet space & updates throughout. Appreciate the outdoors conveniently on your private patio whether it be reading your favorite book, enjoying conversation with family & friends or sipping your favorite drink, from right outside your beautiful kitchen. The rest of the unit has neutral paint & bamboo flooring in the living room with tiled kitchen and hardwood through the second floor, 2 good sized bedrooms. No gas bill, no shoveling or lawn care! The perfect unit for those looking to enjoy simple, maintenance free living. Conveniently located to highways, Longmeadow shops w/ grocery and restaurants, JCC Community Center & Forest Park!
